11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 6-101.23, is
13 amended to read as follows:
14 Section 6-101.23. A. The dismissal, suspension and
15 nonreemployment provisions of the Teacher Due Process Act of 1990
16 shall not apply to:
17 1. Substitute teachers;
18 2. Adult education teachers; and
19 3. Teachers who are employed on temporary contracts.
20 B. The dismissal and suspension provisions of the Teacher Due
21 Process Act of 1990 shall apply to teachers who are employed on
22 temporary contracts for a complete school year and to teachers who
23 are employed in positions fully funded by federal or private
24
